      Elevate your visual storytelling, with FLY.
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600"></p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6 sm:scale-125">
